Kwesé will host a Hearthstone Fireside Gathering at the RUSH eSports event from 21-23 July, with R30,000 up for grabs. Daily Hearthstone tournaments will be held and will award cash prizes to the top three players on each day. The prizes are: Entrants also stand a chance to win an MSI gaming laptop, with the top two players from each day facing off to take home the gaming notebook. There will also be a casual tournament for beginner players. Details are available on the Kwesé Hearthstone website.